GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RegisterFormality> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RegisterFormality> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#RegisterFormality> ;
    narr:childCount "33"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "c354f003fe2a54a8d5d3268a64e6f8923cccb163" ;
    narr:narration """This hub collects observations about register and formality across the corpus. The dominant pattern is **mixed register**: [session-memo code-switching](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_12) between formal analytical prose and informal verbatim blockquotes appears repeatedly — in [ARB call memos](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ARB_ConversationalRegister), [agent-simulation documents](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AgentSim_BlockquoteRegister), [a design collaborator Tokens sessions](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DesignCollaboratorTokensBlockquoteRegister), and [Fable Window planning](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_FableWindowBlockquoteStyle) — identified as Scarlet's session-memo idiolect. A second register cluster is **technical-authoritative**: [infrastructure vocabulary applied to product decisions](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_PerspectiveOrdering_TechnicalRegister) and [engineering-audience prose without definition](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_WriteFlow_TechnicalRegister). A third is **epistemic hedging as declared upfront style**: [conviction-status bolded in headers](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DiscoveryWedge_CaveatEmbedded), [notion-level hedging register](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_NotionLevelCadence), and [provisional flags as both content and form](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ProvisionalFlagVoice). Spoken-transcript children preserve [filler-heavy colloquial speech](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CustomerArchitectColloquialRegister) and [unedited hedges](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_HedgedRegister). The [voice memo register](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_VoiceMemoRegister) adds a stream-of-consciousness variant. No single formality level dominates; the hub spans the full range from zero-hedging declarative to self-critical tentative.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_12> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_8> ;
